<br>
&quot;Hypnos, whether you came by will or force means nothing to your case here. For you have been in our pressence mere moments and have already tried to use your powers against direct daughters of our Mother Gaia whom serve Olympians and mankind alike verywell. You've made yourself out to be irreplaceable and seem to look at yourself higher than that of what you are. We all have our place here Hypnos. Poseidon watches over the Seas, Apollo the sun, Hades the underworld, and I try my best to keep justice in the world fairly. However, you use your powers against those of which you should be helping. Sleep is a great power and mortals need it greatly to live.&quot; She sighed. &quot;But your ego has become greater than the powers of which you posses. You were not to be tried for your actions against the amazons, however since you've brought it up we shall now hold that against you as well.&quot; She stared at him.<br>
&quot;You willingly began a war against mortals and immortals alike. Turned the Gods against one another and because of your hatred for a few women, much blood was spilled. You've disgraced Olympus and the Heavens all together.&quot;<br>
<br>
She looked to Gaia and nodded in respect.<br>
<br>
&quot;The Earth as well. This world was not created for your pleasures. We are Gods and Immortals, we are not here to destroy all that our Mother Gaia and Father Uranus created. We are here to protect it and you have failed to do so. Not only have you attacked the mortals, but your own kinda as well. How do you plead?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 319<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/14/02 6:30:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=260.topic&index=46>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://web.uvic.ca/grs/bowman/myth/images/haifa/h89.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A Stern Warning</span><hr size=1> Poseidon looked on in silence with his chin resting on the back of his cuffed hand in thought. His eyes burned a whole through Hypnos but at the mention of the amazonian war the sea god had to intercede.<br>
<br>
&quot;Athena wait!&quot; he said &quot;Hypnos is to be tried for his abuse of power though he did do such a thing with the amazons. If he is to be tried for that than all else who participated in that war, fighting by his side, myself, and Hecate included must be tried too. That is not the issue at hand now, defeat was punishment enough for our actions though some of us, Hypnos in particular, has not learned his lesson. So he is to be tried, him and his minions for power abuse after the war till the present, even as he does so now.&quot;  <br>
<br>
His gaze shifts from Athena to Hypnos and then the immortal lord speaks words of warning, &quot;Mark my words Hypnos, this is a trial and yet you still make a show of the powers you have. If you want to make it a spectacle to impress some person here then be warned that I shall cripple you for eternity, more so than Hephaestus. You will be the laughing stock of all Olympus, do not doubt my powers, and do not make a mockery of yours here in this court, speak with words or not. Believe me, once I have you in my grasp there is none but almighty Zeus who can save you.&quot;<br>
<br>
Poseidon then nodded to Athena as an invitation to continue on with the trial. <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A> at: 7/14/02 6:36:58 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hypnos>Hypnos </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.backtalk.org/shadowydreamer/anime/zagato1.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 306<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/15/02 6:03:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=260.topic&index=47>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ugh.</span><hr size=1> ***Hypnos sat there.*** <br>
